<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Resolve Company · Solução, Decisão e Execução</title>
<meta name="description" content="Prospecção outbound B2B com inteligência de mercado. 28 toques, 4 canais, reuniões com decisores. Resultado garantido.">
<!-- Troque a URL abaixo pela imagem de preview hospedada no seu domínio (1200x630px) -->
<meta property="og:title" content="Resolve Company">
<meta property="og:description" content="Queremos vender pra você. Sem tráfego pago. ROI positivo ou seu dinheiro de volta.">
<meta property="og:image" content="https://SEUDOMINIO.com.br/og-resolve.png">
<meta property="og:type" content="website">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Archivo+Black&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{
  --bg:#08080A;
  --panel:#101014;
  --panel-2:#16161C;
  --line:#23232C;
  --blue:#2456F5;
  --blue-soft:#4D7BFF;
  --white:#FFFFFF;
  --gray:#9CA0AC;
  --gray-2:#5C5F6A;
  --wa:#25D366;
  --radius:16px;
}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{
  background:var(--bg);
  color:var(--white);
  font-family:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;
  font-size:16px;
  line-height:1.6;
  overflow-x:hidden;
}
body::before{
  content:"";
  position:fixed;inset:0;
  background-image:
    linear-gradient(var(--line) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg, var(--line) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size:56px 56px;
  opacity:.14;
  pointer-events:none;
  z-index:0;
}
main{position:relative;z-index:1}

/* ===== TIPOGRAFIA ===== */
.display{
  font-family:'Archivo Black',sans-serif;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  line-height:.95;
  letter-spacing:-.01em;
}
.eyebrow{
  font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;
  font-size:.72rem;
  letter-spacing:.22em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--blue-soft);
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;
  margin-bottom:16px;
}
.eyebrow::before{content:"";width:22px;height:2px;background:var(--blue)}
.section-title{font-size:clamp(1.9rem,6.5vw,3.2rem);margin-bottom:14px}
.section-lead{color:var(--gray);max-width:560px;font-size:.98rem}
.accent{color:var(--blue-soft)}

/* ===== NAV ===== */
nav{
  position:sticky;top:0;z-index:50;
  background:rgba(8,8,10,.82);
  backdrop-filter:blur(14px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(14px);
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
}
.nav-inner{
  max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;
  padding:14px 20px;
}
.logo{font-family:'Archivo Black',sans-serif;font-size:1.05rem;letter-spacing:.04em}
.logo span{color:var(--blue-soft)}
.nav-links{display:flex;gap:4px;overflow-x:auto;scrollbar-width:none}
.nav-links::-webkit-scrollbar{display:none}
.nav-links a{
  color:var(--gray);text-decoration:none;
  font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:.72rem;
  letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;
  padding:8px 12px;border-radius:8px;white-space:nowrap;
  transition:color .2s;
}
.nav-links a:hover,.nav-links a:focus-visible{color:var(--white)}
a:focus-visible,button:focus-visible{outline:2px solid var(--blue-soft);outline-offset:3px}

.wrap{max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 20px}
section{padding:76px 0}

/* ===== HERO ===== */
.hero{padding:84px 0 64px;position:relative}
.hero::after{
  content:"";position:absolute;top:-120px;right:-180px;
  width:520px;height:520px;border-radius:50%;
  background:radial-gradient(circle, rgba(36,86,245,.22), transparent 65%);
  pointer-events:none;
}
.hero-tag{
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;
  font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:.7rem;
  letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gray);
  border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:100px;
  padding:7px 14px;margin-bottom:26px;background:var(--panel);
}
.hero-tag i{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--blue);display:inline-block;
  animation:pulse 2.4s infinite}
@keyframes pulse{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:.35}}
.hero h1{font-size:clamp(2.6rem,10vw,5.4rem);margin-bottom:22px}
.hero h1 .line2{color:var(--blue-soft)}
.hero p{color:var(--gray);max-width:520px;font-size:1.05rem}

/* ===== GARANTIA ===== */
.garantia{
  margin:38px 0 44px;
  border:1px solid rgba(77,123,255,.5);
  background:linear-gradient(100deg, rgba(36,86,245,.22), rgba(36,86,245,.04) 70%);
  border-radius:var(--radius);
  padding:26px 24px;
  position:relative;overflow:hidden;
}
.garantia::before{content:"";position:absolute;left:0;top:0;bottom:0;width:4px;background:var(--blue)}
.garantia b{
  font-family:'Archivo Black',sans-serif;text-transform:uppercase;
  font-size:clamp(1.3rem,5vw,2rem);display:block;line-height:1.05;
}
.garantia b em{font-style:normal;color:var(--blue-soft)}
.garantia span{color:var(--gray);font-size:.94rem;display:block;margin-top:8px;max-width:520px}

.stats{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:12px}
@media(min-width:760px){.stats{grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr)}}
.stat{
  background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius:var(--radius);padding:22px 18px;
  position:relative;overflow:hidden;
}
.stat::before{content:"";position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:3px;background:var(--blue)}
.stat b{
  font-family:'Archivo Black',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(1.6rem,5vw,2.2rem);
  display:block;line-height:1.1;
}
.stat small{color:var(--gray);font-size:.78rem;line-height:1.4;display:block;margin-top:6px}

/* ===== QUEREMOS VENDER ===== */
.vender{border-top:1px solid var(--line)}
.vender h2{font-size:clamp(2.2rem,8vw,4.2rem)}
.no-ads{
  font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;
  font-size:clamp(.85rem,3vw,1.05rem);
  letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--gray);margin:18px 0 10px;
}
.no-ads strong{color:var(--white)}
.vender .section-lead{margin-bottom:8px}
.steps{display:grid;gap:12px;margin-top:38px}
@media(min-width:760px){.steps{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}}
.step{
  background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius:var(--radius);padding:24px 22px;position:relative;
}
.step em{
  font-style:normal;font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;
  font-size:.7rem;letter-spacing:.18em;color:var(--blue-soft);
  display:block;margin-bottom:12px;
}
.step h3{font-family:'Archivo Black',sans-serif;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:1.05rem;margin-bottom:8px}
.step p{color:var(--gray);font-size:.88rem}

/* ===== ADS ===== */
.ads-grid{display:grid;gap:12px;margin-top:36px}
@media(min-width:760px){.ads-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}}
.ads-card{
  background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius:var(--radius);padding:24px 20px;
}
.ads-card h3{font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}
.ads-card h3 em{font-style:normal;color:var(--gray-2);font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:.75rem}
.ads-card p{color:var(--gray);font-size:.88rem}
.ads-punch{
  margin-top:14px;background:var(--blue);border-radius:var(--radius);
  padding:26px 24px;
}
.ads-punch b{font-family:'Archivo Black',sans-serif;font-size:1.25rem;text-transform:uppercase;display:block;margin-bottom:6px}
.ads-punch span{font-size:.92rem;opacity:.92}

/* ===== CADÊNCIA ===== */
.channels-legend{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:14px;margin:28px 0 18px}
.channels-legend span{
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;
  font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:.72rem;
  letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gray);
}
.dot{width:9px;height:9px;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;flex-shrink:0}
.dot.email{background:var(--blue-soft)}
.dot.call{background:var(--white)}
.dot.linkedin{background:#7BA6FF}
.dot.whats{background:var(--wa)}
.days{
  display:flex;gap:10px;overflow-x:auto;
  padding:6px 2px 16px;
  scroll-snap-type:x proximity;
  scrollbar-width:thin;scrollbar-color:var(--line) transparent;
}
.day{
  min-width:78px;scroll-snap-align:start;
  background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius:12px;padding:14px 10px;
  text-align:center;cursor:pointer;
  transition:border-color .2s, transform .2s;
  border-bottom:3px solid var(--line);
  font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;
  color:var(--white);
}
.day:hover{transform:translateY(-2px)}
.day.active{border-color:var(--blue);background:var(--panel-2)}
.day small{display:block;font-size:.6rem;letter-spacing:.14em;color:var(--gray-2);text-transform:uppercase}
.day b{display:block;font-size:1.15rem;margin:2px 0 8px}
.day .day-dots{display:flex;gap:5px;justify-content:center;min-height:9px}
.cadence-detail{
  background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius:var(--radius);padding:22px;
  min-height:96px;
}
.cadence-detail h4{
  font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:.72rem;
  letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--blue-soft);
  margin-bottom:12px;
}
.touch{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;padding:7px 0;color:var(--gray);font-size:.92rem}
.touch .dot{margin-top:7px}
.cadence-total{
  margin-top:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;
  border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--radius);
  padding:18px 20px;background:linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(36,86,245,.14), transparent 60%);
}
.cadence-total b{font-family:'Archivo Black',sans-serif;font-size:1.9rem;color:var(--blue-soft)}
.cadence-total span{color:var(--gray);font-size:.88rem}

/* ===== TCM ===== */
.tcm-grid{display:grid;gap:12px;margin-top:36px}
@media(min-width:760px){.tcm-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}}
.tcm{
  background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius:var(--radius);padding:26px 22px;
}
.tcm .letter{
  font-family:'Archivo Black',sans-serif;font-size:2.6rem;
  color:var(--blue-soft);line-height:1;display:block;margin-bottom:12px;
}
.tcm h3{font-size:1rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em;margin-bottom:4px}
.tcm h4{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:.7rem;color:var(--gray-2);
  letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:12px;font-weight:400}
.tcm p{color:var(--gray);font-size:.88rem}

/* ===== SOLUÇÕES ===== */
.tabs{display:flex;gap:8px;margin:34px 0 18px;overflow-x:auto;scrollbar-width:none}
.tabs::-webkit-scrollbar{display:none}
.tab-btn{
  background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--gray);
  font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:.74rem;
  letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;
  padding:12px 18px;border-radius:100px;cursor:pointer;white-space:nowrap;
  transition:all .2s;
}
.tab-btn.active{background:var(--blue);border-color:var(--blue);color:var(--white)}
.tab-panel{display:none;background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius:var(--radius);padding:28px 24px;animation:fadein .35s ease}
.tab-panel.active{display:block}
@keyframes fadein{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px)}to{opacity:1;transform:none}}
.tab-panel h3{font-family:'Archivo Black',sans-serif;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:1.3rem;margin-bottom:4px}
.tab-panel .sub{color:var(--blue-soft);font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:16px}
.tab-panel p{color:var(--gray);font-size:.94rem;margin-bottom:18px}
.feat{list-style:none}
.feat li{
  color:var(--gray);font-size:.9rem;padding:9px 0 9px 26px;position:relative;
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
}
.feat li:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.feat li::before{
  content:"";position:absolute;left:2px;top:16px;
  width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:3px;background:var(--blue);
}

/* ===== CASES (depoimentos) ===== */
.cases-grid{display:grid;gap:14px;margin-top:38px}
@media(min-width:860px){.cases-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}}
.tcard{
  background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius:var(--radius);padding:28px 24px;
  display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:20px;
  position:relative;
  transition:border-color .25s, transform .25s;
}
.tcard:hover{border-color:rgba(77,123,255,.5);transform:translateY(-3px)}
.tcard::before{
  content:"\201C";
  font-family:'Archivo Black',sans-serif;
  font-size:4.2rem;line-height:0;
  color:var(--blue);opacity:.85;
  display:block;height:26px;
}
.tcard .quote{font-size:1.02rem;line-height:1.6;color:var(--white)}
.tcard .quote strong{color:var(--blue-soft)}
.metric-row{display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.metric-row b{font-family:'Archivo Black',sans-serif;font-size:2rem;color:var(--blue-soft);line-height:1}
.metric-row span{color:var(--gray);font-size:.8rem}
.person{
  display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:center;
  margin-top:auto;border-top:1px solid var(--line);padding-top:18px;
}
.avatar{
  width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;
  background:linear-gradient(140deg, var(--blue), #12308F);
  font-family:'Archivo Black',sans-serif;font-size:.92rem;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
}
.person b{display:block;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.3}
.person small{color:var(--gray);font-size:.78rem;line-height:1.4;display:block}
.person .prod{
  font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:.62rem;
  letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--blue-soft);
  display:block;margin-top:3px;
}

/* ===== MARCAS ===== */
.marquee{
  overflow:hidden;margin-top:36px;padding:20px 0;
  border-top:1px solid var(--line);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
  -webkit-mask-image:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,#000 10%,#000 90%,transparent);
  mask-image:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,#000 10%,#000 90%,transparent);
}
.marquee-track{display:flex;width:max-content;animation:scrollx 30s linear infinite}
.marquee-track span{
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:44px;padding-right:44px;
  font-family:'Archivo Black',sans-serif;text-transform:uppercase;
  font-size:clamp(1.2rem,4vw,1.7rem);color:#3A3D48;white-space:nowrap;
}
.marquee-track i{width:9px;height:9px;background:var(--blue);border-radius:2px;flex-shrink:0;display:inline-block}
@keyframes scrollx{to{transform:translateX(-50%)}}
.segs{
  display:grid;gap:12px;margin-top:14px;
}
@media(min-width:640px){.segs{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}}
@media(min-width:960px){.segs{grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr)}}
.seg{
  background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--radius);
  padding:24px 20px 20px;text-align:left;cursor:pointer;color:var(--white);
  display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;
  font-family:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;
  transition:border-color .25s, transform .25s;
}
.seg::before{
  content:"";position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;background:var(--blue);
  transform:scaleX(0);transform-origin:left;transition:transform .3s;
}
.seg:hover{border-color:rgba(77,123,255,.45);transform:translateY(-3px)}
.seg:hover::before{transform:scaleX(1)}
.seg .wm{
  position:absolute;right:-8px;bottom:-26px;
  font-family:'Archivo Black',sans-serif;font-size:6rem;line-height:1;
  color:var(--white);opacity:.05;pointer-events:none;user-select:none;
}
.seg b{font-family:'Archivo Black',sans-serif;font-size:.95rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.02em;line-height:1.25}
.seg small{color:var(--gray);font-size:.84rem;line-height:1.5}
.seg em{
  font-style:normal;font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:.62rem;
  letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--blue-soft);
  margin-top:auto;padding-top:6px;
}
.seg.more{
  background:linear-gradient(140deg, rgba(36,86,245,.22), var(--panel) 70%);
  border-color:rgba(77,123,255,.4);cursor:default;
  align-items:center;justify-content:center;text-align:center;gap:4px;
}
.seg.more:hover{transform:none}
.seg.more b{color:var(--blue-soft);font-size:1.5rem}

/* ===== MODAL DEPOIMENTO ===== */
.modal{position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:100;display:none;align-items:flex-end;justify-content:center}
@media(min-width:640px){.modal{align-items:center;padding:20px}}
.modal.open{display:flex}
.modal-backdrop{
  position:absolute;inset:0;background:rgba(4,4,6,.72);
  backdrop-filter:blur(6px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(6px);
}
.modal-card{
  position:relative;background:var(--panel-2);border:1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius:20px 20px 0 0;max-width:540px;width:100%;
  padding:34px 26px 30px;animation:slideup .3s ease;
}
@media(min-width:640px){.modal-card{border-radius:20px}}
@keyframes slideup{from{transform:translateY(34px);opacity:0}to{transform:none;opacity:1}}
.modal-card::after{
  content:"\201C";font-family:'Archivo Black',sans-serif;
  font-size:4rem;line-height:1;color:var(--blue);
  position:absolute;top:18px;left:26px;pointer-events:none;
}
.modal-close{
  position:absolute;top:14px;right:14px;width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:50%;
  background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--gray);
  cursor:pointer;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1;z-index:2;
}
.modal-close:hover{color:var(--white);border-color:var(--gray-2)}
.modal .badge{
  font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:.62rem;letter-spacing:.14em;
  text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--blue-soft);
  border:1px solid rgba(77,123,255,.4);border-radius:100px;
  padding:5px 12px;display:inline-block;margin:34px 0 16px;
}
.modal .quote{font-size:1.02rem;line-height:1.65;margin-bottom:20px}
.modal .quote strong{color:var(--blue-soft)}

/* ===== FOOTER ===== */
footer{
  border-top:1px solid var(--line);padding:44px 0 56px;text-align:center;
}
footer .logo{font-size:1.3rem;margin-bottom:8px}
footer p{color:var(--gray-2);font-size:.8rem;font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase}

.reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(22px);transition:opacity .6s ease, transform .6s ease}
.reveal.in{opacity:1;transform:none}
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){
  html{scroll-behavior:auto}
  .reveal{opacity:1;transform:none;transition:none}
  .hero-tag i{animation:none}
  .marquee-track{animation:none}
  .modal-card{animation:none}
  *{transition:none!important}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <div class="logo">RESOLVE<span>.</span></div>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="#metodo">Método</a>
      <a href="#solucoes">Soluções</a>
      <a href="#cases">Cases</a>
      <a href="#marcas">Marcas</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<main>

<!-- HERO -->
<header class="hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="hero-tag"><i></i>Prospecção ativa não pausa</div>
    <h1 class="display">Sua empresa<br><span class="line2">no radar do<br>cliente certo.</span></h1>
    <p>Seu time de prospecção dedicado. Mais que LDRs, BDRs, SDRs e Closers: um comercial inteiro movido a dados, processo e cadência, que entrega resultado, não promessa.</p>

    <div class="garantia reveal">
      <b>ROI positivo ou <em>seu dinheiro de volta.</em></b>
      <span>Se não fizer sentido pra você, não faz sentido pra gente. Critérios de elegibilidade definidos em contrato.</span>
    </div>

    <div class="stats">
      <div class="stat reveal"><b><span class="count" data-target="400" data-prefix="+">0</span></b><small>empresas atendidas de norte a sul do Brasil</small></div>
      <div class="stat reveal"><b><span class="count" data-target="50" data-prefix="+R$" data-suffix="M">0</span></b><small>em contratos negociados em resultado direto</small></div>
      <div class="stat reveal"><b><span class="count" data-target="300" data-prefix="+" data-suffix="K">0</span></b><small>leads gerados por ano com prospecção multicanal</small></div>
      <div class="stat reveal"><b><span class="count" data-target="28" data-suffix="%">0</span></b><small>de aumento médio de conversão dos clientes ativos</small></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- QUEREMOS VENDER -->
<section class="vender" id="vender">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="eyebrow">Direto ao ponto</div>
